Author: BabyBaphomet_
Text: 10 chicken nuggets isn't even a lot of calories....I could eat those on a low restriction day. Sorry your mom was being a jerk :/ I bet she doesn't even actually know the calorie count for nuggets and just assumed it was really high.

Author: Ohlivvy
Text: I will never understand why people comment on other people's eating habits without permission. It's ridiculous. Like, you don't know how active someone has been, or what they've eaten while you haven't been around... I'm so sorry hum
